701716f-a.title: Bronx: Riverdale Avenue - 256th Street (West)
701716f-a.text:
Riverdale Ave., west side, north from West 256th Street. This
land is part of the S.D. Babcouk Estate.
April 24, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

700387f-b.title: Bronx: 256th Street (West) - Riverdale Avenue
700387f-b.text:
(1)
West 256th Street, west from Riverdale Ave. On the right is the
land of the former S.D. Babcock estate, and on the left, the wall of
the G.P. Morisini estate.
April 24, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The north side of the street about 100 feet west of Riverdale Ave.
April 24, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
